  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bb2\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0b85\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc7\u0b95\u0bbe",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Don't be afraid to join the protest tomorrow - Sarath Benzeka",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Member of Parliament Field Marshal Sarath Fonseka has said that those who are going to participate in the demonstration tomorrow need not have any fear.",
        "Those who will participate in the protest tomorrow need not fear anything. Sarath Fonseka added that if the protestors face any inconvenience, our legal team will stand up for them."
      ],
